- content_for :page_header do
  %h1.title
    Hi. I&rsquo;m an Atlanta based Designer &amp;&nbsp;Developer
  %p.body
    Currently I fill my days working at <a href="http://mailchimp.com">MailChimp</a> building tools with Ruby and doing Front-end&nbsp;Development.


%nav.post-list#anchor-projects

  %h2 Projects:
  - projects.collection.each do |project|
    %a{ href: "#{project.url}" }
      %article.post
        %h1= project.title
        %p= project.short_description

%nav.post-list#anchor-articles

  %h2 Recent Writing:

  - blog.articles.each do |article|
    %a{ :href => "#{article.url}" }
      %article.post
        %h1= article.title
        %p= article.date.strftime('%b %e, %Y')